criteria.exclusion_criteria:
Exclusion criteria included:
1. CNS involvement; 
2. history of HIV infection; 
3. post-transplantation lymphoproliferative disorder; 
4. previous organ transplant and pregnancy; 
5. allergic to rituximab; 
6. The patients disagree to join this study; 
7. Any factor that interfere the patient to participate or complete the study.
